202
00:08:26,996 --> 00:08:30,035
There are many women at home.

203
00:08:30,036 --> 00:08:31,266
(Baek Hyun has two sisters.)

204
00:08:31,536 --> 00:08:33,936
I really love things that men do...

205
00:08:34,336 --> 00:08:36,235
- but also things... - Things that women do.

206
00:08:36,236 --> 00:08:37,535
- that women do. - Right.

207
00:08:37,536 --> 00:08:39,676
I even know this. You got magnet nails.

208
00:08:40,346 --> 00:08:41,405
- I know this... - I'm shocked.

209
00:08:41,406 --> 00:08:42,975
- I know this... - Yes.

210
00:08:42,976 --> 00:08:45,245
because my sister asks me, "What should I do for my nails?"

211
00:08:45,246 --> 00:08:48,286
I say, "You could get matte nails."

212
00:08:48,486 --> 00:08:50,685
My sister says, "Who gets those these days?"

213
00:08:50,686 --> 00:08:52,356
"People get magnet nails."

214
00:08:52,716 --> 00:08:53,925
- That's how you know it. - Yes.

215
00:08:53,926 --> 00:08:55,225
I asked, "What are magnet nails?"

216
00:08:55,226 --> 00:08:56,455
And she said that they really use a magnet.

217
00:08:56,456 --> 00:08:58,196
- Yes. - I was so amazed.

218
00:08:58,926 --> 00:09:00,466
- I couldn't do it myself, though. - Right.

219
00:09:00,896 --> 00:09:02,626
That's funny.

220
00:09:03,436 --> 00:09:05,036
Since you're an outgoing person,

221
00:09:05,536 --> 00:09:07,505
