231
00:09:28,556 --> 00:09:32,025
However, the way I saw you completely changed then.

232
00:09:32,026 --> 00:09:33,096
- Really? - Yes.

233
00:09:34,096 --> 00:09:36,696
I wanted Ji Yeon to feel good.

234
00:09:37,436 --> 00:09:38,935
I might have knocked on the wrong door,

235
00:09:38,936 --> 00:09:42,136
but it wasn't a bad one after all.

236
00:09:43,576 --> 00:09:45,576
He makes people feel comfortable.

237
00:09:45,976 --> 00:09:47,845
I could see Baek Hyun is so sweet...

238
00:09:47,846 --> 00:09:49,406
and he's a genuinely good person...

239
00:09:49,606 --> 00:09:51,176
