254
00:10:27,516 --> 00:10:29,716
I don't think so, now that you said that.

255
00:10:30,256 --> 00:10:31,385
I go like this...

256
00:10:31,386 --> 00:10:33,656
What? Come on.

257
00:10:34,526 --> 00:10:36,786
You're good. You did a good job.

258
00:10:36,896 --> 00:10:38,356
- Did I do a good job? - Yes.

259
00:10:40,326 --> 00:10:41,626
Why are my hands shaking over something like this?

260
00:10:46,366 --> 00:10:48,036
