264
00:10:59,346 --> 00:11:01,216
Why are your hands trembling so much?

265
00:11:01,446 --> 00:11:03,756
- Oh, my gosh. - This is hilarious.

266
00:11:06,316 --> 00:11:08,055
How come you're so bad?

267
00:11:08,056 --> 00:11:09,056
